folder: Central Park West & 104th Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
Central Park West, east side, opposite 104th Street. The work-men are tunnelling under Central Park for the Bronx line of the west side Interborough Rapid Transit subway.
December 1, 1900.
title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 104th Street

folder: Central Park West & 104th Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
Central Park West, east side, opposite 104th Street. The excavation work in progress is for the Bronx line of the west side Interborough Rapid Transit subway.
March, 1901.
